{"word":"G4802 - συζητέω - syzētéō - sood-zay-teh'-o - Dispute","slug":"G4802","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συζητέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>syzētéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>sood-zay-teh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Dispute"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C3;&#x03C5;&#x03B6;&#x03B7;&#x03C4;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - suze&#x0304;teo&#x0304;</b> - <i>sood-zay-teh'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G2212\">G2212</a>; to investigate <i>jointly</i>, that is, <i>discuss</i>, <i>controvert</i>, <i>cavil:</i> - dispute (with), enquire, question (with), reason (together)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4803\">G4803</a>, <a href=\"#/G4804\">G4804</a>"}]}